<hymn_number>11136</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (qwl ly ạ̹yh sẖạgẖl bạlk .. wmkẖlyk msẖ mtṭmn
 wbtsẖtky dạymaⁿạ ḥạlk .. wbtḥsbhạ wbtkẖmn)2
 (sẖklk kdh nạsy ạ̹lhk .. nạsy wʿwdh wklạmh
 wạ̹kẖtbạrạt ạlmạḍy mʿạh .. yạllạ ạ̉ṭlb mnh slạmh)2
 2- (qwl ly fyn frḥẗ qlbk .. lyh wạkẖdạk ạldwạmẗ
 lyh sẖạyl dạymaⁿạ hmk .. rạḥt fyn ạlạ̹btsạmẗ)2
 (sẖklk kdh nạsy ạ̹lhk .. msẖgẖwl ạ̉wy ạ̉wy bẓrwfk
 ạ̉w ʿndk sẖk fy ḥbh .. qwm ṣly wạ̹hzm kẖwfk)2
 3- (qwl ly lyh kẖạyf qlqạn .. msẖ mstmtʿ bḥyạtk
 bqạlk ʿly̱ ạlḥạl dh zmạn .. fyn tsbyḥk wṣlạtk)2
 (sẖklk kdh nạsy ạ̹lhk .. nạsy ạ̹nh mʿạk fy ạlḍyq
 hymsẖyk fwq ạlạ̉mwạj .. ạ̉w yftḥ fy ạlbḥr ṭryq)2
 4- (qwl ly lyh msẖgẖwl bạlnạs .. btrạqb kl tṣrf
 wbqyt ʿly̱ ṭwl ḥsạs .. bqyt gẖryb ạ̉wy mtklf)2
 (sẖklk kdh nạsy ạ̹lhk .. ạlly ṭbʿ fyk bṣmạth
 kẖlqk ʿly̱ ṣwrth wsẖbhh .. ʿsẖạn tḥyạ bnfs ḥyạth)2</lyrics>
<title>qwlly lạ̹yh</title>
</song>